				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I can't catch anything obvious from looking at the code. Which emulator are you using? Does the program crash in other emulators as well? You should try debugging it in FCEUX to see if the CPU is doing what you think it should be doing. Open the debugger and set a breakpoint for, say, reads to $0203. So whenever $0203 is read (which happen right in the middle of the problematic code), the emulator will pause, and from there you can step through the instructions and see what the CPU is doing.</div>

